INSERT INTO
            witness_inputs_fri (
                chain_id,
                l1_batch_number,
                witness_inputs_blob_url,
                protocol_version,
                status,
                created_at,
                updated_at,
                protocol_version_patch
            )
            VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, 'queued', NOW(), NOW(), $5)
            ON CONFLICT (chain_id, l1_batch_number) DO NOTHING
